There are 3 csv files which contain phonebooks of two people.The csv files are in the format (name,number,company).
You have to implement a social graph over these files.


Example queries    
Display Adams first degree connections
Displays Adams all second degree connections
Adams wants to know a contact in Adobe
Adam wants to know all the contacts Yahoo
    
Part 1 of the problem.
1.Read the CSV files.
2.Build the graph
3.Run the queries
    
Part 2 of the problem 
What algorithm is used for printing degree connections for a particular person
What alorith is used for finding a particular person who belongs to a particular company.
    
